The image sequences are provided for personal use and in order to facilitate
basic research. We ask not to use these data in any commercial way. We
appreciate an email message to imsekogs@ira.uka.de indicating who has copied
the data and understand that the source will be acknowledged (KOGS/IAKS
Universitaet Karlsruhe) in case individual frames or results obtained with
these data will be published. We explicitly object against redistribution of
adultered versions of our image sequences in order ro maintain compatibility
of sources in case results obtained by different groups have to be compared.
Any further distribution of these sequences will precede under the same
conditions.
